# Best practices for SvelteKit applications and routing

- Use server-side rendering for improved SEO and performance
- Leverage SvelteKit's file-based routing for clear project structure
- Implement proper error handling with `+error.svelte` pages
- Use Svelte stores for global state management
- Optimize load functions to reduce server load and improve user experience